parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause loss of power, unexpected shifting, and stalling, which can lead to accidents, especially when driving at high speeds.

clutch pedal sticks to the floor
clutch pedal does not return to its normal position

clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
